WEBVTT

1
00:00:31.859 --> 00:00:39.789
Seeing you only made it worse, only we were single. I wouldn't have to worry about it.

2
00:00:39.789 --> 00:00:40.750
Wait, is she?

3
00:00:40.750 --> 00:00:45.420
She's her father in the house. Can I use the bathroom?

4
00:00:45.420 --> 00:00:46.380
Yeah.

5
00:00:46.380 --> 00:00:47.659
I need a cold shower.

6
00:00:47.659 --> 00:00:48.380
Yeah, of course.

7
00:01:08.239 --> 00:01:18.109
Mr. Hart, here I got you some hangover medication you should take it.

8
00:01:18.109 --> 00:01:25.780
Thank you, and you can call me William. Don't go. Stay with me.

9
00:01:25.780 --> 00:01:29.459
I know this might not be the best time to express how I feel,

10
00:01:30.430 --> 00:01:34.670
but after my divorce is finalized, can I ask you out?

11
00:01:36.260 --> 00:01:43.459
You should rest, and I have set up the couch for you.

12
00:01:43.459 --> 00:02:00.129
My god, what did he just say?

